{"body": "If we're going to have to do the \"legacy cookie jar\" upgrade path thing again, I'd like to try to slip signing the cookie name into the value as well.\r\n\r\nIts kinda scary that you could swap the cookie value from some other value into an auth token.\r\n\r\n``` ruby\r\ncookies.signed[:user_id] = 42\r\ncookies.signed[:referrer_id] = params[:referrer_id] # 42\r\n\r\ncookies[:user_id] == cookies[:referrer_id]\r\n```", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/20766190", "created_at": "2013-07-10T19:20:22Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/11168#issuecomment-20766190", "updated_at": "2013-07-10T19:20:22Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 11168, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/josh/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/josh/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/josh/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/josh", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/josh/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/josh", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/josh/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/bbe5dc8dcf248706525ab76f46185520?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F3988c7f88ebcb58c6ce932b957b6f332.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/josh/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/josh/received_events", "gravatar_id": "bbe5dc8dcf248706525ab76f46185520", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/josh/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "josh", "type": "User", "id": 137, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/josh/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5237d81cbd3543c151008457"}, "id": 20766190, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/11168"}
